{"tid":1903081,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"我最期待的畫面出現了.jpg","createTime":"2020-02-28T17:36:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T17:53:31.000Z","uid":105567,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"68da884cdbf0d48aecdcff6e73c90cc8298d57b0","tid":1903081,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T17:36:57.000Z","msg":"光榮冰室FB PAGE<br />\n<br />\n話說上年12月5日，一名女子在尖沙咀一間食店，在已付款的情況下，拿錯了一碟叉燒炒蛋飯及一件多士。這是店鋪疏忽。客人詢問後，店員迅速作出調查，了解當時情況，並在顧客的協助下檢視有關的order。<br />\n<br />\n小編一直期待，有市民會留意光榮專業調查案件，並拍照留念，與網民開心分享。想不到，這個畫面今天真的出現了！ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NHbkWz9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNHbkWz9.jpg&h=2b492ba8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#店舖疏忽<br />\n#有人落錯單求助<br />\n#認真工作的店員非常Charming"},{"pid":"17662d4900f53c7e137d53fb371f9fdab8125d30","tid":1903081,"uid":92783,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T17:40:37.000Z","msg":"笑死 識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9379aa761f78c63f0f3163c574b4fab5b4ad239d","tid":1903081,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T17:43:44.000Z","msg":"句嘢唔係咁用架😅"},{"pid":"fb0d701ea7d70f696ba0c0c1e59731df66d5c67f","tid":1903081,"uid":105567,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9379aa761f78c63f0f3163c574b4fab5b4ad239d","tid":1903081,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T17:43:44.000Z","msg":"句嘢唔係咁用架😅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T17:44:57.000Z","msg":"詳見香港警察FB PAGE"},{"pid":"eca322d1166a32bb5e013df183c232e1f85beb01","tid":1903081,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"fb0d701ea7d70f696ba0c0c1e59731df66d5c67f","tid":1903081,"uid":105567,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9379aa761f78c63f0f3163c574b4fab5b4ad239d","tid":1903081,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T17:43:44.000Z","msg":"句嘢唔係咁用架😅"},"citedBy":1,"